# =======================================================
# CLINE-OPTIMIZED FILE AND FOLDER EXCLUSIONS
# =======================================================

# 1. Recursive Blocks (Catches folders hidden deep inside subdirectories)
**/node_modules/**
**/dist/**
**/dist-ssr/**
**/build/**
**/out/**
**/.cache/**

# 3. Block Heavy Media and Binaries (Zero value for AI context)
*.mp4
*.png
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.gif
*.svg
*.pdf
*.zip
*.tar.gz
